. We verify these trends with\npost-processing of 1D models and show that these trends are reflected in model\nsynthetic spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2013 20:00:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 May 2014 17:29:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
