articular, we show how to get from the solution of one of the\nproblems to the other. We illustrate the results with explicit examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2013 07:46:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Dec 2013 12:26:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 6 Sep 2015 08:15:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-08"}
