 to solve the problem with the same complexity, or better. The other\nalgorithms are as efficient as the best known algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2013 14:09:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2013 10:16:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-18"}
